The paper deals with graph algorithms and their implementation on MapReduce, which suggests that it could belong to categories related to data structures (cs.DS), distributed computing (cs.DC), data mining (cs.DM), databases (cs.DB), and social and information networks (cs.SI). The focus on connected components and clustering further supports these categories.
